dct_title_s: Contrafehtung der fürnemen Statt Venedig : sampt den vmbligenden Inseln
dct_description_sm: Map of Venice; relief shown pictorially. Appears in a German ed. of Münster's Cosmographia, published sometime between 1544 and 1628. Pages cclvi-cclvii from: Cosmographiae universalis lib. VI / Sebastian Munster. Basel : Officin Henricpetrina, [ca. 1550]. German text and page nos. on verso: Die Statt Venedig ... cclviii, cclv.
